OL,3,CMan killed wife before taking own life
OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,FA coroner has ruled that a jeweller
OL,7,Fsuffered a "psychotic episode" after
OL,8,Fnot taking his medication, when he
OL,9,Fkilled his wife before taking his own
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FThe bodies of Christopher Stone-
OL,13,FHoughton, 66, and Ruth Stone-Houghton,
OL,14,F60, were found at their home in Holcot
OL,15,FLane in Portsmouth, on September 14
OL,16,F2022.
