OL,3,CMan killed wife before taking own life
OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,FSpeaking today the couple's children
OL,7,Fsaid their deaths were "entirely
OL,8,Favoidable" and have called on the
OL,9,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting to take
OL,10,Faction, saying "the lessons from this
OL,11,Fmust be addressed nationally."
OL,13,FPost-mortem examinations found Mr
OL,14,FStone-Houghton died as a result of
OL,15,Fsuspension, and the cause of death of
OL,16,FMrs Stone-Houghton, who was found with
OL,17,Fa claw hammer next to her body, was a
OL,18,Fhead injury.
