OL,6,FShe said that she found his discharge
OL,7,Fin August was "unsafe due to an
OL,8,Finadequate risk assessment concerning
OL,9,Fthe care plan" put in place, but said
OL,10,Fshe did not find this to be "causative
OL,11,For contributory" to the deaths.
OL,13,FMs Spearing said that in the weeks
OL,14,Fbefore the couple's deaths, Mr Stone-
OL,15,FHoughton had shown signs of
OL,16,Fimprovements and "no physical
OL,17,Fmanifestations of anxiety".
