OL,3,CMan killed wife before taking own life
OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,FShe said: "All indicators were that he
OL,7,Fwas making a positive recovery,
OL,8,Fcomplying via a routine with
OL,9,Fmedications, denying any suicidal
OL,10,Fthoughts with hope, positive
OL,11,Finteractions with friends and future
OL,12,Fplanning.
OL,14,F"There was never any expressed
OL,15,Findication or history of genuine
OL,16,Fconcern for his harming Ruth."
OL,18,FBut the coroner said that toxicology
OL,19,Ftests carried out as part of the post-
OL,20,Fmortem examination showed that he had
OL,21,Fnot been taking his medication.
OL,26,@nD@KOUvD@AOU
