OL,6,FDescribing the couple, she added:
OL,7,F"Ruth and Christopher Stone-Houghton
OL,8,Fwere described as 'a fun, loving
OL,9,Fcouple who did everything together and
OL,10,Fadored their children, whom they were
OL,11,Fvery close to'.
OL,13,F"Both were loyal friends who were
OL,14,Falways helping others, and the events
OL,15,Fof last September were described as 'a
OL,16,Fcomplete shock to us all'."
