OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,FThe inquest also heard that Mr Stone-
OL,7,FHoughton held a gun licence for three
OL,8,Frifles and a pistol, which he used at
OL,9,Fa gun club, but he had handed this
OL,10,Fover to a registered firearms dealer
OL,11,Fin June 2022.
OL,13,FThe coroner said that the police had
OL,14,Fcontacted his GP after a concern was
OL,15,Fraised about his ownership of
OL,16,Ffirearms, but the doctor had not
OL,17,Freplied because Mr Stone-Houghton had
OL,18,Ftold his doctor that he no longer had
OL,19,Fneed of the licence.
