OL,6,FMs Spearing said she found it
OL,7,F"concerning" that there was no
OL,8,Fmandatory requirement for a GP to
OL,9,Fnotify police of their concerns but
OL,10,Fadded it had not contributed to the
OL,11,Ftwo deaths.
OL,13,FIn a separate inquest into Mr Stone-
OL,14,FHoughton's death, Ms Spearing recorded
OL,15,Fa narrative conclusion that he had
OL,16,F"ended his life" while suffering a
OL,17,F"psychotic episode".
