OL,6,F"More than three years after losing
OL,7,Fthem, nothing could have prepared us
OL,8,Ffor the emotional toll of hearing
OL,9,Fevidence during the past week of
OL,10,Fdisjointed care, inaction, inadequate
OL,11,Frisk assessments and missed
OL,12,Fopportunities. It has been
OL,13,Fretraumatising. We couldn't have got
OL,14,Fthrough this week without the family
OL,15,Fand friends who have filled the court
OL,16,Fdaily to support us.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/18
