OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F416A1765884855
OL,3,CMan killed wife before taking own life
OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,F"Throughout our Dad's illness, we saw
OL,7,Fthat our parents did not receive the
OL,8,Fhelp they were entitled to and
OL,9,Fdeserved, despite our desperate
OL,10,Fefforts to secure support. The
OL,11,Fseverity of Dad's illness was not
OL,12,Frecognised, nor was Mum's role as a
OL,13,Fcarer. These failures to truly see
OL,14,Fthem and their needs cost them their
OL,15,Flives and their deaths were entirely
OL,16,Favoidable. They should be with us here
OL,17,Ftoday, enjoying their first
OL,18,Fgranddaughter and looking forward to
OL,19,Fthe birth of another grandchild in the
OL,20,FNew Year.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
