OL,6,F"Nothing will ever dimmish the love we
OL,7,Ffeel for both our parents. We couldn't
OL,8,Fhave wished for better. We miss them
OL,9,Fevery day, but we are determined to go
OL,10,Fforward positively in our lives in the
OL,11,Fway they taught us.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
