OL,3,CMan killed wife before taking own life
OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,F"We welcome the changes now in place
OL,7,Ffor those using the services of
OL,8,FHampshire and Isle of Wight NHS Trust.
OL,9,FHowever, it is deeply troubling that
OL,10,Fthese changes came only as a result of
OL,11,Fthe deaths of our parents, and too
OL,12,Flate to save them. Their deaths should
OL,13,Fnot have been the catalyst for action.
OL,14,FWe hope these changes lead to lasting
OL,15,Fimprovements and prevent other
OL,16,Ffamilies from suffering the
OL,17,Fdevastating and avoidable loss that we
OL,18,Fhave.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/18
