OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F416A1765884855
OL,3,CMan killed wife before taking own life
OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,F"We say this directly to the Health
OL,7,FSecretary, Wes Streeting: this inquest
OL,8,Fhas exposed serious failings in the
OL,9,Fprovision of mental health services.
OL,10,FThe lack of care our Mum and Dad
OL,11,Freceived was not an isolated or local
OL,12,Fincident, and the lessons from this
OL,13,Fmust be addressed nationally. We
OL,14,Feagerly await the coroner's rulings on
OL,15,FPrevention of Future Deaths reports.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
