OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F416A1765884855
OL,3,CMan killed wife before taking own life
OL,4,Cduring psychotic episode, inquest hears
OL,6,F"We were a close and loving family, no
OL,7,Fdifferent from countless others.
OL,8,FPlease do not assume it cannot happen
OL,9,Fto your family. It can happen to
OL,10,Fanyone. To families seeking help for a
OL,11,Floved one with mental ill health:
OL,12,Ftrust your instincts. You know them
OL,13,Fbest. If you are not being heard, keep
OL,14,Fpushing. Mental ill health is
OL,15,Fisolating and overwhelming, and
OL,16,Ffamilies should not have to battle a
OL,17,Fsystem that is not fit for purpose. By
OL,18,Fspeaking out, we hope others recognise
OL,19,Fthe signs earlier and keep asking for
OL,20,Fhelp until it is taken seriously.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
